item.description:
@Jason321 wrote:

yay, stop advertising meatspin lol.[br][size=1]Posted at: December 06, 2006, 11:55:57 PM[/size][hr]ok. Goto server advertisement on the forums. Look for peoples threads. Find 1 you like. Click on it and it will say something like examplescape.no-ip.info…Goto www.moparisthebest.com or if you already have it downloaded, open it up. Ok now on the top left corner i think it is there will be a file button click file>new server ip or something>then type in the server’s ip that your trying to login to. Now type any username and pass and click login. There, your done.

item.title: How can i log on to someone's server?
item.dc:creator: @TheShadow TheShadow
item.description:
@TheShadow wrote:

Open up you’re moparscape then go here to get the server status to servers http://moparisthebest.hostinplace.com/serversatus.php. Once u have ur moparscape open go to “File” then click “New Server” Then type the name of the server and then make a name and a password then loging if it says “Error connection to server.Must be down Click “cancel” Then start server to make ur own” just try another server I hope this helps u P.S if u host ur own server without a source only u can play on it and know one else can
